HEADWORD: Superfrontal
<hw>Su`per*fron"tal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Eccl.)</fld>
<def>A cloth which is placed over the top of an altar, and often hangs
down a few inches over the frontal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

